overview: This sequel to Paranormal Retreat 1 is just as crazy and scary, will JB ever find his Team and Madam Della, I don't think so, what he encounters on this property and deep woods is horrifying! JB has been hospitalized on and off for over a year, the cops are out to get him, they think he is somewhat crazy or is he? Watch the horror unfold and ask yourself is it real or not?
title: Paranormal Retreat 2-The Woods Witch
